window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Narrated by Scott Eastwood and Andi Arndt, a sweeping, second chance romance that weaves mystery, passion, and humor as two present-day lovers search for a love story from the past....</b></p> <p>Past loves should stay in the past.</p> <p>After the way my first love took off for the ends of the earth, the last thing I want is to see him on billboards and bookstore bestseller shelves. Now my boss just handed me the project that could make my career. All I have to do is partner up with the man, the myth, the legend - adventurer Hunter Armstrong.</p> <p>That's easier said than done, because when we reconnect, I learn Hunter has his own agenda on this project. And it's not to find a treasure in art and antiques. It's me. But what we discover shocks both of us, and we have no choice but to follow the clues....</p> <p><i>P.S. It’s Always Been You: Part 1 </i>is the first installment in the P.S. It's Always Been You serial novel. Presley and Hunter’s story continues in <i>P.S. It's Always Been You: Part 2</i>.</p>"; 
